{"tid":12790,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"屌佢老母，我條IM50又斷針啦屌那星，邊到有線買？","createTime":"2016-11-29T20:55:11.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T12:00:00.000Z","uid":26249,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d36dd3e38d45243db219d12b1044ed75d4f8c788","tid":12790,"uid":26249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T20:55:11.000Z","msg":"仆佢個街 上年買到依家<br />\n個零月之前先去左原廠保養換番條線<br />\n屌那星 上星期又整斷左 有冇咁易斷呀<br />\n已經勁小心用 屈耳骨位個陣都勁驚斷<br />\n一個on9唔小心 訓教個陣放左係褲袋冇拎出黎<br />\n訓醒就斷撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問下邊到有得買過條線？<br />\n我對換線零認識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係巴打們會建議我買過個其他既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依排冇乜錢，其實本身都冇乜錢架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係afford到好低階既 ~$100-200<br />\n有冇推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇乜特別要求 音質同im50咁上下就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a02ff55c7bcd77d0dc652bacdef8e16f7edc434","tid":12790,"uid":26249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T20:56:50.000Z","msg":"btw 個im50係上年減價個陣買<br />\n好似$399 <br />\n係咪我買到伏野先咁易斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0520d4f358a76c5fa98c69017f022d483952dfd","tid":12790,"uid":3628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T21:13:49.000Z","msg":"點解唔買個耳機盒裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65afa4074fb43fb36fbf0b32ad708786bc9b487d","tid":12790,"uid":18930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T21:18:48.000Z","msg":"講真 真係好難斷針 冇睇過im50線唔知邊條好<br />\n利申 im50一出即買<br />\n<br />\n你筆直咁低 得通利 清貨上代高登神器klipsch s3 s4差唔多<br />\n<br />\n入盒啦"},{"pid":"26b844c8de032961a69e938bf7267b0a1d87929e","tid":12790,"uid":26249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:37:25.000Z","msg":"換番條線一定會入盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c73fc0e9454846e59807579e9c03b8eebc7e8cf","tid":12790,"uid":15410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/151811_fb6f9d9672a47a014f89e1f05677264b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F151811_fb6f9d9672a47a014f89e1f05677264b.jpg&h=ccdc5608&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原廠線連線控 300蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上個月加入im50大家庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f084d151b61b553c2dd5165a03d590114a2a3527","tid":12790,"uid":35651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:22:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"00b58b2f9d0f32762184e0877a8724fa35f3dfb8","tid":12790,"uid":26249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:22:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/151811_fb6f9d9672a47a014f89e1f05677264b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F151811_fb6f9d9672a47a014f89e1f05677264b.jpg&h=ccdc5608&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原廠線連線控 300蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上個月加入im50大家庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加